Dialogue: 0,00:00:27.12,00:00:30.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）ヨタ！　頼む。\Nやめてくれってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.11,00:00:32.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:34.12,00:00:36.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！！\N《サクラ：ナルト！》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:36.14,00:00:39.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サクラちゃん？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:39.25,00:00:42.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あんた　ヨタって言ったわよね？\Nそっちにも来てるの？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you just say "Yota"?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he there too?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:42.95,00:00:45.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《そっちって…　サクラちゃんの\Nところにもいるのかよ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean, "there too"?{\i0}\N{\i1}He's with you also?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:45.93,00:00:47.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《シカマル：サクラどころじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only Sakura!{\i0}\N{\i1}But with us too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:47.95,00:00:50.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺たちのところにも\Nキバのところにも…》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Including Kiba!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.63,00:00:53.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《キバ：あぁ…\N派手にやってくれてるぜ》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh boy... He's really going at it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.99,00:00:57.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタが４人…》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are four Yotas?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.32,00:01:00.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《チョウジ：ヨタ　怒ってるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Yota is angry at us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:00.17,00:01:02.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから　みんなのところに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe that's why he came to each of us.{\i0}\N{\i1}Because we let him die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.48,00:01:05.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,僕たちのせいで\N死んじゃったから…》
Dialogue: 0,00:01:05.48,00:01:07.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタは　幽霊じゃねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yota is not a ghost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:07.44,00:01:09.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穢土転生で操られてんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was reanimated{\i0}\N{\i1}and is being controlled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:09.47,00:01:11.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しっかりしろ　チョウジ》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get your act together, Choji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:11.46,00:01:13.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ちょっと　待てよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on a sec!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.53,00:01:15.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穢土転生って　影分身みたいに\Nそんなにいっぱい→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So with Reanimation,{\i0}\N{\i1}you can be resurrected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:15.57,00:01:17.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よみがえらせることが\Nできんのかよ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lots of times like Shadow Clones?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.46,00:01:19.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《これまでは　なかったが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not until now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.49,00:01:23.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《俺が　相手してんのは\N間違いなくヨタだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm positive it's Yota I'm facing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:23.63,00:01:26.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ\Nみんなのところにいるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means, all of you could{\i0}\N{\i1}be seeing that white guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:26.46,00:01:29.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの　白いヤツかも\Nしれねえってばよ》
Dialogue: 0,00:01:29.78,00:01:31.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,白ゼツか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, White Zetsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.78,00:01:33.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,本物じゃないってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's not the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.84,00:01:36.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも　この雪はヨタの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But this snow is Yota's...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.48,00:01:39.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや　本体が術をかけてりゃ\N問題ねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the real one is\Nperforming the jutsu, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:39.53,00:01:43.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,というより　ヨタを操ってる誰かだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say,\Nthe one controlling Yota.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.52,00:01:46.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな　きっとそいつらは\Nヨタじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... These guys aren't Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.65,00:01:50.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから\Nみんなが苦しむことなんかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need to feel guilty!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.10,00:01:52.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,痛みは　俺が引き受ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take on your guilt! So...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.01,00:01:57.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから　倒しちまってくれ。\Nニセモンのヨタを！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them down...\NTake down the Yota impostors!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.03,00:02:00.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
