Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.97,00:03:56.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.87,00:03:58.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,超倍化の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Expansion Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:01.03,00:04:03.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,影真似の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.21,00:04:10.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.95,00:04:29.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ニセモンとはいえよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he is an impostor...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:29.74,00:04:31.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いくぜ　赤丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:48.71,00:04:52.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ざけんなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:52.10,00:04:54.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はぁ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:08.26,00:05:10.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.76,00:05:21.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あのとき俺たちは\Nヨタを助けようとした。　けど…》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, we tried to save Yota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:05:24.08,00:05:26.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((また　１人か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm alone again...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.53,00:05:30.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,じゃねえよ。　６人と１匹だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's six of us plus one dog!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:30.39,00:05:33.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなで来ちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We all came.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:33.60,00:05:36.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なっ…　あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What—?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:36.45,00:05:39.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前ら！\N人んちにズカズカと入るんじゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! You can't just\Nwalk in uninvited...!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.11,00:05:42.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何言ってんの。\N今まで寂しそうにしてたくせに。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no way to talk.\NYou looked so lonely right up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:42.88,00:05:45.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ったく　いい天気だってのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... It's so nice outside...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.61,00:05:49.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,部屋の中いると　ますます誰も\N寄りつかなくな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay cooped up like this,\Nno one will want to...?!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:49.06,00:05:52.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん？　雨が降ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.27,00:05:54.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（２人）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:59.12,00:06:01.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Yota?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:01.15,00:06:03.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺たちで　ヨタを奪い返すんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get Yota back!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:25.64,00:06:30.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どこから来た？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.11,00:06:33.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どこの里だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What village?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:33.15,00:06:37.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私　わからないよ…　難しいこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know...\Nabout complicated stuff...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:37.83,00:06:41.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,優しいこと言ってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me easy questions.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.20,00:06:46.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どこから来た？　どこの里だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? What village?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:50.64,00:06:52.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,埒が明かないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:52.99,00:06:56.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,手荒になる前に\N一度　三代目にお越し願おうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We should ask Lord Third to come\Nbefore things get more intense.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:16.57,00:07:20.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《幻術？　いや…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it genjutsu...? No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:23.02,00:07:26.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ギャーッ　ハハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.36,00:07:31.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,コラ！　やめろ！\N下りてこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down from there!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.72,00:07:35.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,バーカ！　誰が下りるかってぇの！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! As if I'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.56,00:07:39.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は　うずまきナルト！\N忍者だってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Naruto Uzumaki! I'm a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:39.00,00:07:41.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（火影）なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.10,00:07:45.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヤツは　問題の少年と一緒にいた\Nアカデミー生徒の１人です。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of the students\Nfrom the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who was with the boy in custody.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:48.12,00:07:51.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,捕まえられるもんなら\N捕まえてみろってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:51.41,00:07:55.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里中の忍者　みんなこ～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All the ninja in the village!\NCome and get me!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.82,00:07:59.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,待て　この悪ガキが！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,– That damned brat!\N– Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:59.21,00:08:02.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天気雨…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun showers?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.40,00:08:05.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まったく！\Nなんてバチ当たりなヤツだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a pain in the butt...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:05.37,00:08:09.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目様の顔岩は\Nそりゃあ　もうメチャクチャらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Lord Third's\NMountainside Image
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:09.41,00:08:11.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうらしいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:11.41,00:08:14.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この里で暮らしていながら\Nなぜ　そんなことができるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in our village.\NHow could he do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:14.70,00:08:17.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アタッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:17.29,00:08:19.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（２人）おっ？
Dialogue: 0,00:08:21.88,00:08:24.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か見た？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:24.44,00:08:28.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや…　ハハッ　気のせいだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:28.33,00:08:30.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:32.57,00:08:36.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お願いだから　もう助けてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you. Let me go...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.58,00:08:40.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…　うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.95,00:08:51.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,影真似の術　成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu complete!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:51.91,00:08:55.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヨタ！　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yota! Hey!\N– Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey! Yota!\N– Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:55.12,00:08:57.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おい！\N大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,00:08:57.17,00:08:59.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.13,00:09:03.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:03.13,00:09:05.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヒヒヒヒッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:05.10,00:09:07.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やっぱりすごいよ　シカマル！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru, you're amazing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.29,00:09:10.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大人の忍者に\N術をかけちゃうなんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a jutsu on grown-up ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.21,00:09:12.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（いの）アンタ　ひょっとして天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you some kind of genius?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:12.52,00:09:15.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや　まだまだひよっこだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope... He's still wet behind the ears.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:19.98,00:09:22.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:22.04,00:09:24.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,動くな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:24.29,00:09:29.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里の利益をおびやかす者は\N子供といえど　容赦はしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who threatens\Nthe welfare of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will be treated harshly,\Neven if they are children.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:29.03,00:09:31.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,コイツは　スパイかもしれないんだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be a spy.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:35.35,00:09:37.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be joking!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:39.77,00:09:43.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,コイツは…　ヨタは　そんなんじゃねえ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:45.99,00:09:49.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタは…　俺の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota is... the first friend...\NI've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:49.34,00:09:52.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の初めてできた友達だ！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.77,00:09:55.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,友達…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.41,00:10:00.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:20.02,00:10:25.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わ…　私の…　友達！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... My friend...!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:40.06,00:10:42.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:42.05,00:10:44.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,逃げるってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:05.04,00:11:07.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,深ぇぞ　この川。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This river is deep.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:07.43,00:11:10.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも　ここを越えないと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to cross it...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:10.09,00:11:12.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう追っ手が向かってるはずよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably coming\Nafter us already.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:12.74,00:11:15.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,水の上が渡れたら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could walk on water...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.13,00:11:17.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（キバ）行くっきゃねえよ！\N（赤丸）ワンワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:17.72,00:11:22.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,行こう。　ヨタを自由なところへ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go someplace\Nwhere Yota can be free!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.95,00:11:42.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.95,00:11:44.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ガハッ…。\Nナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:04.51,00:12:07.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チョウジ！　シカマル！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,– Choji!\N– Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,– Shikamaru!\N– Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:17.79,00:12:20.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,プハッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.54,00:12:23.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yota!\N– Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:27.48,00:12:30.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハア…　ハア…　ゴホッ　ゴホッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:30.55,00:12:34.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハア…　ハア…　ハア…。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.12,00:12:37.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　ありがとな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:37.23,00:12:39.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota?!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:41.17,00:12:43.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヨタ！！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:46.13,00:12:54.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((みんな：ヨタ！　ヨタ！　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yota! Yota!\N– Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yota!\N– Yota! Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yota!\N– Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.13,00:12:56.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:59.22,00:13:01.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.22,00:13:03.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ？\Nヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.95,00:13:07.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しっかりして！\N（チョウジ）平気？　寒くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.07,00:13:10.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！　もう　大丈夫だから。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.93,00:13:13.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。\Nしっかりしなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:13.78,00:13:15.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（赤丸）クゥーン…。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:18.77,00:13:23.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よかったね　みんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:23.07,00:13:27.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう　大丈夫だからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:27.07,00:13:32.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前がだよ！\Nしっかりしてくれよ。　なぁ　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're the one who's okay!\NSnap out of it, Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:32.12,00:13:36.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私は　もう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.11,00:13:38.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ダメだよ。　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:38.65,00:13:43.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ごめん。　俺が　ムチャしなけりゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nif I hadn't been so reckless...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:43.09,00:13:46.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺のせいだ。\Nクゥーン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.26,00:13:49.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もっと　いい手があったはず…\Nなのによ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've tried a different way...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.84,00:13:54.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！\Nヨタ…　ごめん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota... I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.47,00:14:00.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お別れだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:00.47,00:14:05.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何　言ってんだよ！？\Nこれからも　俺たちは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we're...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:05.13,00:14:09.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私は　みんなのこと　忘れない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:09.54,00:14:15.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも　みんなは\N私のこと　忘れるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys, forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:15.17,00:14:17.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,バカなこと　言ってんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:17.88,00:14:22.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忘れるわけ　ないだろ！\N（シカマルたち）そうだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we forget you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yeah, he's right!\N– It's true, Yota!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:27.51,00:14:31.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忘れなきゃ　つらいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forget...\Notherwise... it will be painful.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:37.90,00:14:40.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　俺は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:45.16,00:14:47.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヨタ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo... ta...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:47.87,00:14:51.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《そして　俺たちは　ヨタを忘れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so we forgot about Yota...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:51.84,00:14:55.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,楽しかった　すべてを。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About all the fun we had...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.84,00:14:59.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなと友達だったことも。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That we were all friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was alone once again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:59.58,00:15:03.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は　ひとりぼっちに戻った》
Dialogue: 0,00:15:08.84,00:15:12.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　俺は忘れたくなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to forget you...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:12.89,00:15:15.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前とのこと　忘れるくらいなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather live with\Nthe guilt of letting you die...!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:15.54,00:15:19.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前を死なせた後悔の中で\N生きてたほうが　よっぽど…。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:19.97,00:15:23.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう一度…　もう一度　ヨタを→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota, do I have to...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:23.91,00:15:27.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんな目に\Nあわせなきゃなんねえのかよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,make you suffer one more time?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:34.63,00:15:37.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,耐えられるわけ　ないだろ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I bear that?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:51.90,00:15:53.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:56.89,00:16:00.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…　私だよ　ヨタだよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto... It's me. Yota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:00.31,00:16:02.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yota...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's our secret tin can telephone...{\i0}\N{\i1}just between you and me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.24,00:16:09.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルトと私の秘密の糸電話だよ》
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.28,00:16:13.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《これなら\N穢土転生の術者に聞かれずに…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoever is controlling him{\i0}\N{\i1}won't be able to hear us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:13.24,00:16:15.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…　アンタの頭の中のその声！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto! That voice inside your head!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.95,00:16:17.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ！》\N《２人：ヨタ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}– Yota!{\i0}\N{\i1}– Yota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:17.97,00:16:20.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタじゃねえか！》\N《ワン！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Yota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura! Shikamaru! Ino!{\i0}\N{\i1}Choji! Kiba! Akamaru!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:20.39,00:16:25.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サクラ　シカマル　いの　チョウジ　キバ　赤丸》
Dialogue: 0,00:16:25.10,00:16:28.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ごめん　ごめん…　ごめんね》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry... I'm sorry...{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm so sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you apologizing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:28.52,00:16:30.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《なんで謝るの？》
Dialogue: 0,00:16:30.96,00:16:35.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《俺たちは　お前を\N助けることができなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We couldn't save you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We let you die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:35.38,00:16:38.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死なせちまったんだ。\Nだから　みんな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why everyone's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto... Everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:38.97,00:16:41.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルトもね　みんなもね→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry yourselves over that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.00,00:16:44.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,気にすることなんか\N何もないんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because when I met you guys,{\i0}\N{\i1}I was already dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:44.30,00:16:48.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だって　私はね\Nナルトたちに会ったとき→
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.03,00:16:50.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう　死んでたんだもん》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was reanimated,{\i0}\N{\i1}then I met you guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.30,00:16:56.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《穢土転生でよみがえって\Nそれで　ナルトたちに会ったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.69,00:17:01.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう死んでたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was already dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,WEATHER FOR SALE
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.15,00:17:07.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私は　天気を操る不思議な\N力を持った一族に生まれて→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was born into a clan that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}possessed the strange ability{\i0}\N{\i1}to control weather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,DISTANCE: 2.44 MILES
Dialogue: 0,00:17:07.63,00:17:13.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,天気売りを商売にして\N里から里へ旅して歩いた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We went from village to village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selling weather was our trade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.89,00:17:20.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私　一族のなかでも　特に\N天気使いがうまかったんだよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in my clan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was especially good{\i0}\N{\i1}at controlling the weather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:26.50,00:17:31.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《でもね　生まれつき\N体が弱くってね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I was born very weak...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:31.21,00:17:34.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死んじゃったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:34.20,00:17:40.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死んだんだけど\N呼び止められちゃった》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I died, but... I wasn't allowed to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.42,00:17:55.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((キャーッ！))
Dialogue: 0,00:18:03.34,00:18:06.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《カブト：ヨタ　役立てよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yota... Be useful now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:06.57,00:18:11.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ：蛇とメガネがね\N穢土転生のテストだっていって→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The snake... and the glasses fellow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They said they were{\i0}\N{\i1}testing Reanimation and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:11.21,00:18:15.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルトたちの里に\N私を置いていったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they left me in your village, Naruto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:15.23,00:18:18.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私はね　悲しかった》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was... so sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:18.21,00:18:21.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yota...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.23,00:18:26.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サクラ：ホントに　ごめんね。\N一緒にいてあげられなくて》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yota... We're so sorry{\i0}\N{\i1}we couldn't stay with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no, don't be sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.09,00:18:29.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ううん　謝ることないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, it was so tough{\i0}\N{\i1}when I was alive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:29.44,00:18:34.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのね　私　生きてるとき\Nつらくて　つらくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was always alone,{\i0}\N{\i1}no matter where I went.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:34.27,00:18:37.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どこにいても\Nずっと　ひとりぼっちだった。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:37.63,00:18:42.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でもね　死んでから\Nひとりぼっちじゃなくなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But after I died,{\i0}\N{\i1}I wasn't alone anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:42.05,00:18:47.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなに会って\Nホントに楽しかったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I met all of you...{\i0}\N{\i1}And it was so much fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:47.60,00:18:51.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの川で　また\Nよみがえってしまったけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was resurrected at{\i0}\N{\i1}that river once more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:51.89,00:18:57.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれからまた１人で　死にながら\N生き続けてきたけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I had to live alone all over again,{\i0}\N{\i1}although I was dead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.67,00:19:01.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなとの思い出があるから\Nつらくなんかなかった》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I had my memories of{\i0}\N{\i1}all of you, so it wasn't hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's too bad it had to be this way...{\i0}
